[size=14pt][b][color=#FF00FF]WHY THIS MATTERS[/color][/b][/size]

[b]1. Data Integrity is Non-Negotiable[/b]
On a blockchain, data corruption means lost funds. The race conditions we fixed could theoretically cause block orphaning under high load. v2.2.0 eliminates this risk entirely.

[b]2. 12-Week Roadmap is Engineering-Driven[/b]
Each phase targets a specific, measurable bottleneck. No vaporware - just systematic optimization with clear metrics.

[b]3. Named Phases for Accountability[/b]
SCRAMJET, LAMINAR, HOHMANN, SLINGSHOT, KALMAN, DELTA-V - each phase has a name, timeline, and expected outcome. Track our progress week by week.

[b]4. Foundation Before Speed[/b]
We fixed the data integrity issues FIRST, before launching the optimization roadmap. A fast database that corrupts data is worthless.

